oads/UNDI406NMPBKB_p114109_23862.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UNDI406NMPBKB_p114109_23863.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UNDI406NMPBKB_p114109_23864.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UNDI406NMPBKB_p114109_23865.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UNDI406NMPBKB_p114109_23866.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UNDI406NMPBKB_p114109_23867.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UNDI406NMPBKB_p114109_23868.jpg\", \"https://us.ilve.com/wp-content/uploads/UNDI406NMPBKB_p114109_31698.jpg\"], \"Variant Price\": \"9940.00\", \"Variant Barcode\": \"8051202531443\", \"Variant URLS\": \"\", \"Variant Count\": \"\", \"Variant HTML\": \"      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel station-tabs-default-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_description\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_description\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\"><div class=\\\"product-desc\\\"><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Nostalgie</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The taste of tradition, with a modern twist.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The perfect blend of past and present, creating the very heart of your home. Nostalgie is the range of cooking systems that combines elegant retro aesthetic inspiration with cutting edge technologies.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Nostalgie range cookers integrate highly professional technologies and excellent materials with a classic style that is always inspiring. Undisputed protagonists of the kitchen, they offer a complete choice of sizes (from 30 to 60 inches) and various configurations: you can choose the flush-top induction up to 6 cooking zones with bridge function for 48 inches version, single or double oven, standard colors or RAL colors on request, various finishes and accessories. Only available as an option for the Nostalgie collection, Noblesse frames are more than just a detail: they are a fine design feature that frames the front panels, matching the metallic finishes of the handles and knobs. The blind door inspired by the past is another option that elegantly enriches the style of Nostalgie.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><ul style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><li>Residual heat indicator</li><li>Timer with automatic stop</li><li>Bridge control</li><li>Booster function</li><li>Slide controls</li><li>Child safety</li><li>Overheating and liquid spill protection</li><li>Precise electronic temperature control</li><li>Door and drawer with soft-closing system</li><li>Quick start\\u00a0</li></ul><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><hr><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Product Technologies</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p>Aesthetics is important, but that\\u2019s not all. It is essential to have the best technologies available to cook well and with pleasure. ILVE puts all its experience and research at your service, offering solutions that combine top-level performance and maximum simplicity, safety and user-friendliness: to always guarantee the best satisfaction.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Cooktop (Hob) Technologies</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Induction Cooktop (Hob)</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Nostalgie induction cooktops (hobs) are a safe, fast and functional way of cooking, using the latest technology combined with a sleek and refined design. Ease of cleaning, energy saving, safety, versatile temperature control and cooking speed are some of the advantages that induction provides, helping to facilitate the preparation of dishes and recipes.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Residual Heat Indicator</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Indicates that the glass is hot and therefore, one should be careful when touching it and when placing items on it as they might be damaged.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Timer with Automatic Stop</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Turns off the active zone once the set time elapses.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Bridge Control</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Induction cooktops (hobs) that have this feature, provide the option of simultaneously controlling 2 adjacent zones with a single command as if they were a single zone.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Booster Function</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Allows you to focus all the power of the induction cooktop (hob) in the preset zone, to speed up the boiling and cooking times.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Slide Controls</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">This handy \\u201ctouch control\\u201d system makes it possible, for example, to increase or decrease the operating temperature by sliding your finger from right to left or vice versa.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Child Safety</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Once this function has been set and until it is disabled, the induction cooktop (hob) does not turn on by turning on the controls.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Overheating and Liquid Spill Protection</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">If the cooktop (hob) overheats or liquid spills occur, a safety device trips and stops operation.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><hr><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Oven Technologies</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>The ovens: Grand Size and Performance.</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Any single or double combination oven you choose, will provide you with all the space you need, even for large dishes.\\u00a0Our 40-inch range has an oven capacity up to 4 cubic feet.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Quick Start</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Reach your desired temperature in a short time with the quick preheating function, then choose the best cooking mode suited for your dish. It also works as rapid defrosting when set at a low temperature.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Precise Electronic Temperature Control</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The electronic control ensures that the temperature of the oven remains constant throughout, without fluctuating, as is the case in conventional ovens.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Door with Soft Closing System</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The door hinges are fitted with a shock absorber that makes closure more gradual and noiseless.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Primary Oven Functions: UOV 60\\u00a0M</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><ul style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><li>Pizza function</li><li>Quick start</li><li>Multiple fan cooking</li><li>Intensive cooking</li><li>Fan grill cooking</li><li>Grill cooking with closed door</li><li>Cooking from above</li><li>Cooking from below</li><li>Static normal cooking</li></ul><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Secondary Oven Functions: UOV 40 E</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><ul style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><li>Grill cooking with closed door</li><li>Cooking from above</li><li>Cooking from below</li><li>Static normal cooking</li></ul><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><hr><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Oven Functions</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Pizza Function</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Suitable for baking pizza, but also for bread and focaccia. The main source of heat is the lower heating element which, with the help of the other underpowered heating elements, creates an ideal situation for this type of cooking.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Quick Start</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">The quick oven preheating function allows it to reach the desired temperature in a short time and you can then choose the best suited cooking mode for the dish.\\u00a0It also works as rapid defrosting when set at a low temperature.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Multiple Fan Cooking</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">This is the function that allows different dishes to be cooked simultaneously without the smells mixing. Lasagna, croissants and brioches, tarts, cakes, etc. can be baked, thereby saving time and electricity.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Intensive Cooking</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">It assures quick and intensive cooking with steam discharge. It is recommended to obtain a crispy result: baked potatoes and vegetables, chicken, salt crusted fish, etc.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Fan Grill Cooking</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Particularly fast and deep, with significant energy savings, this function is suitable for many foods, such as: pork chop, sausages, pork or mixed kebabs, game, Roman-style gnocchi, etc.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Grill Cooking with Closed Door</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Recommended function for quick and deep grilling, browning and roasting meat in general, fillet, Florentine steak, fish and even vegetables.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Cooking from Above</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">Particularly suitable for browning and adding the final touch of color to many foods; it is the recommended function for burgers, pork chops, veal steaks, sole, cuttlefish, etc.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Cooking from Below</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">\\u200bThis is the most suitable cooking method to complete the cooking cycle, especially pastries (biscuits, meringues, leavened desserts, fruit desserts, etc.).</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>Static Normal Cooking</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">This is the classic function of the electric oven, particularly suitable for cooking the following foods: pork chop, sausages, salt cod, braised meat, game, roast veal, meringues and biscuits, baked fruit, etc.</p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><hr><table class=\\\"table table-bordered o_table\\\"><tbody><tr><td><p><span class=\\\"h2-fs\\\"><strong>Customize Your Range</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\\\"table table-bordered o_table\\\"><tbody><tr style=\\\"height: 44.25px\\\"><td><p><strong>Knobs\\u00a0<strong>and Handle Bundles</strong></strong></p></td><td><p>EN40P62211\\u00a0(Copper), EN40G62211\\u00a0(Brass), EN40B62211 (Burnished), EN40C62211\\u00a0(Chrome)</p></td></tr><tr style=\\\"height: 54px\\\"><td><p><strong>Handles</strong></p></td><td><p>EA4270009000020 / EA4270071000020 (Copper),\\u00a0EA4270009000016 /\\u00a0EA4270071000016 (Brass),\\u00a0EA4270009000018 /\\u00a0EA4270071000018 (Burnished),\\u00a0EA4270009000008 / EA4270071000008 (Chrome)</p></td></tr><tr style=\\\"height: 54px\\\"><td><p><strong>Knobs\\u00a0</strong></p></td><td><p>Standard Knobs \\u2013 EG9493002000120 (Copper),\\u00a0EG9493002000116 (Brass),<br>EG9493002000118 (Burnished),\\u00a0EG9493002000108 (Chrome)<br>Temperature Knobs \\u2013\\u00a0EG9494005000120\\u00a0(Copper),\\u00a0EG9494005000116 (Brass),<br>EG9494005000118\\u00a0(Burnished),\\u00a0EG9494005000108 (Chrome)<br>Oven Function Knobs \\u2013\\u00a0EG9488014000120\\u00a0(Copper),\\u00a0EG9488014000116 (Brass),\\u00a0EG9488014000118\\u00a0(Burnished),<br>EG9488014000108 (Chrome)</p></td></tr></tbody></table><hr><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong><strong>Limited 2 Year Parts and Labor Warranty</strong></strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\"><strong>California Proposition 65</strong></p><p style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px\\\">WARNING: Cancer and Reproductive Harm</p><p><a href=\\\"http://www.P65Warnings.ca.gov\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">www.P65Warnings.ca.gov</a></p></div>.<br><br><strong>Freight Charges May Apply</strong><br><br></div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" data-slug=\\\"accessories\\\" role=\\\"tab\\\" aria-selected=\\\"false\\\" tabindex=\\\"-1\\\"> <span class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtext\\\">Accessories</span> </span></h3>      <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel\\\" id=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_accessories\\\" aria-labelledby=\\\"station-tabs-tab_accessories\\\" role=\\\"tabpanel\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\">         <div class=\\\"station-tabs-tabcontent\\\">                     </div>      </div>      <h3 class=\\\"station-tabs-tabtitle\\\"><span id=\\\"station-tabs-tab_videos\\\" class=\\\"station-tabs-tab\\\" aria-controls=\\\"station-tabs-tabpanel_videos\\\" data-slug=\\\"videos\\\" role=\\\"ta